 heres one more thought of FV for you too compare to your server.<br>When you see a dark elf and high elf pass each other on the road and they both scowl at each other at the same time as they run by you know youve truly entered norrath.<br>&nbsp;<br>Gatsu<br>28th season warrior<br>Firionia vie<br>"I am not a twink try and keep that in mind"</td></tr>
